text: Kristen Jeannine Dalton-Wolfe (born December 13, 1986) is an American actress from North Carolina who won the Miss USA 2009 pageant. She also finished tenth at the Miss Universe 2009 pageant after this. Category:1986 births Category:Beauty pageant winners Category:Actors from North Carolina Category:Living people
